{"tid":1112580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"patrick beverley完美示範咩係舊式NBA粗獷防守","createTime":"2019-04-17T12:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:11:39.000Z","uid":209890,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4247248d6448707de503f9564e7d6f8f98d2ccc","tid":1112580,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"老一代NBA球員成日話依加防守力度廢<br />\n話自己打依加NBA既話可以場場入50分<br />\n依加既人係舊時NBA實打唔出水準<br />\n因為以前NBA防守係好可以好粗暴<br />\n依加佢就同你講<br />\n認真貼身少少防守<br />\nKD就已經頂唔順<br />\n依加NBA對抗性真係好差<br />\n真係想像唔到以前壞孩子軍團防守有幾暴力<br />\n波神要一個面對晒佢地<br />\n一入去就比人MMA<br />\n正因為以前防守咁暴力<br />\n所以波神開發左背籃進攻 因為下下衝入籃底分分鐘收山<br />\n可惜依加人人衝入去就有罰球射<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FVzWfxxqEwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFVzWfxxqEwU&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=90ad4c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FVzWfxxqEwU</a><br />\n守到KD發脾氣"},{"pid":"01efbae6f544099b03aee540d27f422254f431a3","tid":1112580,"uid":3408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇佢守波<br />\n打防守嘅熱血"},{"pid":"abeb5a04362f6af9cf25df6aa8c7ea036242b993","tid":1112580,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01efbae6f544099b03aee540d27f422254f431a3","tid":1112580,"uid":3408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇佢守波<br />\n打防守嘅熱血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"估唔到kd係怕矮仔<br />\n因為矮仔夠快<br />\n可以貼到實一實<br />\n貼到咁實你都唔敢跳<br />\n萬一比佢攝腳就重傷"}]}